{"tid":569915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【玻璃心碎晒】台男籃名將IG發「台灣台北」球衣照 遭強國網民辱罵","createTime":"2018-02-23T07:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T12:37:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bfa84be28bbbdfd73949349b3fd9886f1bee21","tid":569915,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519364822_2562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519364822_2562.jpg&h=e6ff0d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被稱為「護國神Q」的台灣籃球員戴維斯（Quincy Davis），昨在日本完成世界盃亞洲區資格賽預賽後，在IG發佈了一張PS照片，可見其球衣上的「中華台北」（Chinese Taipei）被改為「台灣台北」（Taiwan Taipei），讓台網民大讚，大陸網民則玻璃心碎一地，很多人還翻牆到IG辱罵他。<br />\n<br />\n現年35歲的戴維斯，於2013年放棄美國國籍，歸化台灣，並成為台首名歸化的球員。昨日他不僅帶領台灣逆轉擊敗日本，賽後還在IG上po出一張他穿着「台灣台北」球衣的照片，並留言：「偉大的勝利」。「勝利」除可解讀戴維斯在昨日比賽上取得出12分、11個籃板及6次助攻，還能解讀為他自己改圖的「Taiwan」球衣。<br />\n<br />\n照片上傳後，台灣網民大讚「Team Taiwan」、「太棒了Q」、「I love you Q！Love Taiwan」、「謝謝你這麼支持台灣」、「Proud of you（以你為榮）」。不過，這張照片卻氣壞了大陸網民，不少人翻牆到戴維斯的IG上留言辱罵，很多都是極粗鄙的言語，令台網民看不過眼：「我們不要理沒水準的人！」<br />\n<br />\n戴維斯對台灣情有獨鍾，先前Nike發表台灣隊新球衣時，球衣上面有「Chinese Taipei」的縮寫「CT」，戴維斯當時沒看仔細，以為只有T字，讓他高興地說：「球衣上面終於出現台灣了」，可惜最後是空歡喜一場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180223/57865443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57865443&d=nGmPlKXyr6%2Bq9HMFUFVD5br9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=0154deb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57865443&h=1f03d3d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180223/57865443</a>"},{"pid":"6d635621a610f38857ae2615c328999b75ea2d0e","tid":569915,"uid":12021,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1fef8fbd4127f8c0de1a7ff68a6541fb116e1c8","tid":569915,"uid":76314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"人地著咩關你班支狗咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9bc7feea1039a709c88ff4df550b536a0ba1ed","tid":569915,"uid":67237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"班中國人幾時著返唐裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75aa80d6788ab2988b69b7018f07e3eca86001a8","tid":569915,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c9bc7feea1039a709c88ff4df550b536a0ba1ed","tid":569915,"uid":67237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"班中國人幾時著返唐裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"北佬著胡服"},{"pid":"41fe19ced98462e603bf096e588a582d89e4a809","tid":569915,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"人地又唔係黃頭髮黑皮膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}